        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer31199878" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1278584238025473954">Amazing, existentialist book. If it were possible, this book should be printed on translucent pages. In the end, the words remain and rise into being, floating in the world. May be his best in many years. Gorgeous, sad, full of love--I could go on with hyperbole--this book makes me happy to be alive and in the presence of such a writer.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


